        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Aug 12. 76</date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir,</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am very much obliged for your handsome present of “Recherches sur les Veg. Fossile &amp;c”, which adds one more to the many gifts for which I am greatly indebted to you.<ref target="#foot.f1"/></p>
<p>With sincere respect | Yours very faithfully | Charles Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
        </div>

        

        

        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">CD’s copy of <hi rend="italic">Recherches sur les végétaux fossiles de Meximieux</hi> (Research on the fossil plants of Meximieux; Saporta and Marion 1876) is in the Darwin Library–CUL.</note>
        </div>        
            
